dct_title_s: Fishermen's chart, Gaza - el Arish / compiled and drawn by E. Rosenau
dct_description_sm: Depth shown by soundings. Government of Palestine. Dept of Agriculture and Fisheries. Fisheries Service. "Reproduced & printed by the Survey of Palestine, Jaffa 1938." "This chart is based upon British Admiralty Charts with the permission of the Controller of H.M. Stationery Office and of the Hydrographer of the Navy; and upon the maps of the Department of Lands and Surveys, Palestine, with the permission of the Commissioner."
